  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Jak czytać ten dashboard",
      "datasource": null,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Korelacja UI ↔ Loki**\n- Gracz wysyła nagłówek `X-UI-Trace-Id` (chip **cli·** w czacie).\n- Backend zwraca `X-Turn-Id` i loguje je jako `turn_id` (chip **srv·** na dymku „myśli”).\n- Zapis tury: `narrative_turn` ma **`turn_id`** i **`ui_trace_id`** (w treści panelu poniżej).\n- **Explore — filtr po kliencie:**\n```\n{service=\"backend\"} | json | event=\"narrative_turn\" | ui_trace_id=\"<wklej-uuid>\"\n```\n\n**SSE (postęp przed finalnym tekstem)**\n- Na backendzie: **`SSE_NARRATIVE_PROGRESS_LOG=1`** → logi `sse_narrative_progress` (co ~25 chunków).\n\n**Walka**\n- `dice_roll` z `source` = `combat_attack` / `combat_enemy`, pola `dc`, `outcome`.\n\n**Resety (dev)**\n- `campaign_progress_reset`, `character_progress_reset` (przyciski Reset kamp. / Reset post.)."
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Start streamu narracji (turn_stream_open)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "PD5A68A3BD6F8BA56"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "options": {
        "dedupStrategy": "none",
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "showCommonLabels": true,
        "showLabels": false,
        "showTime": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "PD5A68A3BD6F8BA56"
          },
          "expr": "{service=~\"$service\"} | json | event=\"turn_stream_open\" | campaign_id=~\"${campaign_id}\"",
          "queryType": "range",
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Postęp tokenów SSE (sse_narrative_progress — wymaga SSE_NARRATIVE_PROGRESS_LOG=1)",
